OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,FAccess to an old cricket ground has
OL,7,Fbeen legally restricted in an attempt
OL,8,Fto tackle illegal waste dumping.
OL,10,FIt comes after a nearby site on,
OL,11,FBolton House Road in Wigan, was turned
OL,12,Finto a 25,000 tonne fly-tipping site,
OL,13,Fmaking it one of the largest illegal
OL,14,Fwaste dumps in the country.
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency then found
OL,17,Fscrap metal was being removed from the
OL,18,FBolton House Road site and moved onto
OL,19,Fthe old cricket ground in Bickershaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
