PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,FThey sought a restriction order from
OL,7,FWigan Magistrates' Court which will
OL,8,Fprohibit anyone from importing waste
OL,9,For accessing the premises for six
OL,10,Fmonths. Failure to comply with the
OL,11,Fcourt order is a criminal offence.
OL,13,FMark Easedale, Area Environment
OL,14,FManager at the Environment Agency,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We've taken action to restrict
OL,16,Faccess to this land as part of our
OL,17,Fongoing response to the nearby illegal
OL,18,Fwaste site at Bolton House Road.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,F"We have immense sympathy for the
OL,7,Flocal community affected by this waste
OL,8,Fcrime, which continues to have an
OL,9,Fimpact on the people who live and work
OL,10,Fin the area.
OL,12,F"We are doing everything within our
OL,13,Fpowers to identify the perpetrators,
OL,14,Fincluding launching a major criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation and interviewing
OL,16,Findividuals under caution."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
