PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,FThe two-acre site sits next to houses,
OL,7,Fa playing field and a primary school.
OL,8,FRubbish was first dumped on the site
OL,9,Fin October 2024, piling it up to 20
OL,10,Fmetres high.
OL,12,FNisha Roson, who lives close by, told
OL,13,FITV News in January that the dump
OL,14,Fattracts seagulls, flies and rats.
OL,16,FShe said: "The rats have gone
OL,17,Fcompletely out of control. We've had
OL,18,Frats in our cars, rats in our houses,
OL,19,Fwe see them wandering around on our
OL,20,Fstreet, they're just always about."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
