OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,FThe illegal rubbish tip previously
OL,7,Fcaught fire in 2025, and burned for 10
OL,8,Fdays.
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency is working in
OL,11,Fpartnership with Wigan Council,
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police and Greater
OL,13,FManchester Fire and Rescue Service to
OL,14,Fhelp manage the illegal Bickershaw
OL,15,Fdump.
OL,17,FThey have already interviewed a number
OL,18,Fof people under caution and formal
OL,19,Fnotices have been served requiring the
OL,20,Fwaste to be removed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
