PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772287406
OL,3,CAccess to land restricted to tackle
OL,4,Cillegal waste dumping
OL,6,FThe criminal investigation is ongoing.
OL,8,FAny members of the public who have
OL,9,Finformation relating to the illegal
OL,10,Fdeposit of waste at this site should
OL,11,Fcall the Environment Agency incident
OL,12,Fnumber on 0800 80 70 60.
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
